It also includes, as an addendum, shrines that existed at the time the ''Engishiki'' Jinmyōchō was compiled but are not recorded in it, the so‑called {{ill|Shikigaisha|de|Shikigaisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|zh|Shikigaisha|12=draft}}.
--> == Shikinai Shrines (式内社) == In the ''Engishiki'' Jinmyōchō, a total of 11 shrines are recorded – one major shrine (Myojin Taisha) and ten minor shrines (Shosha).
