manuelle|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/User talk:Immanuelle|qq=}}) 05:34, 17 March 2025 (UTC)}} '''{{ill|List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|de|List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|ja|下総国の式内社一覧|zh|List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|lt=List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|lt_ja=しもうさのくにのしきないしゃいちらん|lt_de=List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|lt_zh=List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province|qq=}}''' (下総国の式内社一覧) This is a list of shrines recorded in the volumes 9 and 10 of the ''Engishiki'' “Jinmyōchō (Upper and Lower)” ({{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|zh|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=}}) – namely, the so‑called {{ill|Shikinaisha|de|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|2=ja|3=式内社|qq=draft|1=Shikinaisha|zh|Shikinaisha|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikinaisha|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikinaisha|qq=}} and their {{ill|candidate shrines|de|candidate shrines|ja|論社|1=candidate shrines|2=ja|3=論社|lt=candidate|zh|candidate shrines|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/candidate shrines|13=User:Immanuelle/candidate shrines|qq=}} – that are classified as part of Shimōsa Province.
It also includes, as an addendum, shrines that existed at the time the ''Engishiki'' Jinmyōchō was compiled but are not recorded in it, the so‑called {{ill|Shikigaisha|de|Shikigaisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|zh|Shikigaisha|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigaisha|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigeisha|qq=}}.
