It also includes, as an addendum, shrines that existed at the time the ''Engishiki'' Jinmyōchō was compiled but are not recorded in it, the so‑called {{ill|Shikigaisha|de|Shikigaisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|zh|Shikigaisha|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigaisha|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigeisha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 延喜式神名帳|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}.
