{{afc comment|Wikidata entry [[d:Q11361283]]}} This is a '''List of Shikinaisha in Shimōsa Province''' or the list of shrines in [[Shimōsa Province]] which is present in the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=}}
On this page we will also cover the {{ill|Shikigeisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigeisha|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigeisha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 延喜式神名帳|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} of [[Shimōsa Province]] which are shrines that are known to have existed at that time due to other historical records, such as the [[Rikkokushi]], but for some reason were excluded from the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=}}. We will cover them in a separate list to avoid confusion.== Shikinaisha (式内社) == {| class="wikitable sortable" ! Prov !! Name !! Kana !! Rank |- | 1 || {{ill|Katori Shrine|WD=Q372380}} || かとりじんぐう || Myojin Taisha |- | 2 || {{ill|Samukaha shrine|WD=Q135039756}} || サムカハ || |- | 3 || {{ill|Sogahime-jinja|WD=Q11625202}} || そがひめじんじゃ || Shikinai Shosha |- | 4 || {{ill|Oio-jinja|WD=Q11610638}} || おいおじんじゃ || Shikinai Shosha |- | 5 || {{ill|Makatano shrine|WD=Q135039757}} || マカタノ || |- | 6 || {{ill|Takahashi Shrine|WD=Q11670742}} || || Shikinai Shosha |- | 7 || {{ill|Takedasuga Shrine|WD=Q11387225}} || たけだすがじんじゃ || Shikinai Shosha |- | 8 || {{ill|Kuwabara-jinja|WD=Q70203929}} || || Shikinai Shosha |- | 9 || {{ill|Morono shrine|WD=Q135039758}} || モロノ || |- | 10 || {{ill|Ōhi Shrine|WD=Q3090870}} || おおひじんじゃ || Shikinai Shosha |- | 11 || {{ill|Mitsuchino shrine|WD=Q135039759}} || ミツチノ || |- | || {{ill|Shikinaisha|WD=Q134917286}} || || |- | || {{ill|Shikinai Taisha|WD=Q134917288}} || || |- | || {{ill|Shikinai Shosha|WD=Q134917287}} || || |}
